<span>Alex,</span> <span>AI</span> <span>PM</span> <span></span></h2></P></div><div data-framer-name=\"Background\"><p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"397\" height=\"322\" src=\"https://framerusercontent.com/images/aYhFE5z0YrjieJ8h7I90mdZZ4.png?width=397&height=322\" alt=\"\"></p><div data-framer-name=\"Gradient+Blur\"><p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"418\" height=\"431\" src=\"https://framerusercontent.com/images/7vmuSdT9w91pmP3Mx2ut8kqG8d8.png?width=418&height=431\" alt=\"\"></p></div></div></div><div data-framer-name=\"Bento Top\"><div data-framer-name=\"Background\"><p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"397\" height=\"322\" src=\"https://framerusercontent.com/images/aYhFE5z0YrjieJ8h7I90mdZZ4.png?width=397&height=322\" alt=\"\"></p><div data-framer-name=\"Gradient+Blur\"><p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"418\" height=\"431\" src=\"https://framerusercontent.com/images/HBYBlvyKAZoXeoJvIqPjp4lqM.png?width=418&height=431\" alt=\"\"></p></div></div><div data-framer-name=\"Bento Header\"><P data-framer-component-type=\"RichTextContainer\" data-framer-name=\"The All-in-One\"><h2 dir=\"auto\"><span>Meet</span> <span>Sam,</span> <span></span><br><span>AI</span> <span>Engineer</span></h2></P><P data-framer-component-type=\"RichTextContainer\" data-framer-name=\"Designed to help you focus on what matters most—collaboration, clarity, and action.\"><h3 dir=\"auto\">A copy change, a website update, a broken automation, a report someone pulls by hand every week: the small technical stuff that waits because there's no one to do it. Anyone on the team can hand it to Sam. Sam and Alex work together directly, so the plan and the work never drift apart. Sam remembers your product as it goes, so nothing has to be explained twice. If your team ships software, Sam takes on the bigger work too: features, bug fixes, PRs, and the review back and forth.</h3></P></div></div></div><section data-framer-name=\"Benefits Section\"><div data-framer-name=\"Container\"><div data-framer-name=\"Left Align\" id=\"features\" data-border=\"true\"><div data-framer-name=\"Math / Trend Up\"><p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"16\" height=\"17\" src=\"https://framerusercontent.com/images/qWG9prLwso6E66Ql2i9cGT31I.svg?width=16&height=17\" alt=\"\"></p></div><p data-styles-preset=\"kIj6AEGZU\">FEATURES</p></div><P data-framer-component-type=\"RichTextContainer\" data-framer-name=\"The All-in-One\"><h2 data-styles-preset=\"tCpDylYM9\" dir=\"auto\"><span>Alex</span> <span>and</span> <span>Sam</span> <span>come</span> <span>pre-built.</span> <span>No</span> <span>prompts,</span> <span>no</span> <span>training,</span> <span>running</span> <span>in</span> <span>minutes.</span></h2></P></div><div data-framer-name=\"Bento Top\"><div data-framer-name=\"Background\"><p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"397\" height=\"322\" src=\"https://framerusercontent.com/images/aYhFE5z0YrjieJ8h7I90mdZZ4.png?width=397&height=322\" alt=\"\"></p><div data-framer-name=\"Gradient+Blur\"><p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1618\" height=\"970\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) max((100vw - 264px) / 2, 1px), (min-width: 810px) and (max-width: 1199.98px) calc(100vw - 96px), (max-width: 809.98px) calc(100vw - 32px)\" srcset=\"https://framerusercontent.com/images/hzzbCTKmJMAQFstLO5bKyXByFb4.png?scale-down-to=512&width=1618&height=970 512w,https://framerusercontent.com/images/hzzbCTKmJMAQFstLO5bKyXByFb4.png?scale-down-to=1024&width=1618&height=970 1024w,https://framerusercontent.com/images/hzzbCTKmJMAQFstLO5bKyXByFb4.png?width=1618&height=970 1618w\" src=\"https://framerusercontent.com/images/hzzbCTKmJMAQFstLO5bKyXByFb4.png?width=1618&height=970\" alt=\"\"></p></div></div><div data-framer-name=\"Bento Header\"><P data-framer-component-type=\"RichTextContainer\" data-framer-name=\"Designed to help you focus on what matters most—collaboration, clarity, and action.\"><h3 dir=\"auto\">Read the full conversation thread for any task, between agents and with your team. See a timestamped log of every action taken. Nothing runs in the dark.</h3></P></div></div></section></div></DIV>","content_text":"Meet Alex and Sam. They run your product and ops, manage projects and tickets, make fixes, remember every decision, and ask you before anything goes out.Meet Alex, AI PM Meet Sam, AI EngineerA copy change, a website update, a broken automation, a report someone pulls by hand every week: the small technical stuff that waits because there's no one to do it. Anyone on the team can hand it to Sam. Sam and Alex work together directly, so the plan and the work never drift apart. Sam remembers your product as it goes, so nothing has to be explained twice. If your team ships software, Sam takes on the bigger work too: features, bug fixes, PRs, and the review back and forth.FEATURESAlex and Sam come pre-built. No prompts, no training, running in minutes.Read the full conversation thread for any task, between agents and with your team. See a timestamped log of every action taken. Nothing runs in the dark.","fetched_at":"2026-07-22T06:59:37.948Z","ok":true,"blocks":[{"html_en":"<p dir=\"auto\"><span><span>M</span><span>e</span><span>e</span><span>t</span></span> <span><span>A</span><span>l</span><span>e</span><span>x</span></span> <span><span>a</span><span>n</span><span>d</span></span> <span><span>S</span><span>a</span><span>m</span><span>.</span></span> <span><span>T</span><span>h</span><span>e</span><span>y</span></span> <span><span>r</span><span>u</span><span>n</span></span> <span><span>y</span><span>o</span><span>u</span><span>r</span></span> <span><span>p</span><span>r</span><span>o</span><span>d</span><span>u</span><span>c</span><span>t</span></span> <span><span>a</span><span>n</span><span>d</span></span> <span><span>o</span><span>p</span><span>s</span><span>,</span></span> <span><span>m</span><span>a</span><span>n</span><span>a</span><span>g</span><span>e</span></span> <sp