 the dark.</h3>","sentences":[{"en":"Read the full conversation thread for any task, between agents and with your team.","zh":"阅读代理之间以及与您的团队之间任何任务的完整对话线索。"},{"en":"See a timestamped log of every action taken.","zh":"查看所采取的每个操作的带时间戳的日志。"},{"en":"Nothing runs in the dark.","zh":"没有什么在黑暗中运行。"}]}],"translated":true,"content_html_zh":"<div class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div data-framer-root=\"\"><header data-framer-name=\"Hero section\"><div data-framer-name=\"Container\"><div data-framer-name=\"Heading\"><p dir=\"auto\">认识亚历克斯和山姆。 他们运行您的产品和运营，管理项目和票证，进行修复，记住每一个决定，并在任何事情发生之前询问您。</p></div><div data-border=\"true\" data-framer-name=\"Dashboard Wrapper\"><p><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"2214\" height=\"1574\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) max(min(max(min(100vw - 93px, 1240px), 1px), 1111px), 1px), (min-width: 810px) and (max-width: 1199.98px) max(min(max(min(100vw - 93px, 1240px), 1px), 1111px), 1px), (max-width: 809.98px) 355.8717px\" srcset=\"https://framerusercontent.com/images/U9ufO3gi4aCwqRuTU04qx89f6h4.png?scale-down-to=512&width=2214&height=1574 512w,https://framerusercontent.com/images/U9ufO3gi4aCwqRuTU04qx89f6h4.png?scale-down-to=1024&width=2214&height=1574 1024w,https://framerusercontent.com/images/U9ufO3gi4aCwqRuTU04qx89f6h4.png?scale-down-to=2048&width=2214&height=1574 2048w,https://framerusercontent.com/images/U9ufO3gi4aCwqRuTU04qx89f6h4.png?width=2214&height=1574 2214w\" src=\"https://framerusercontent.com/images/U9ufO3gi4aCwqRuTU04qx89f6h4.png?width=2214&height=1574\" alt=\"Dashboard Mockup\"></p></div></div></header><div data-framer-name=\"About Section\"><div data-framer-name=\"Bento Top\"><div data-framer-name=\"Bento Header\"><p data-framer-component-type=\"RichTextContainer\" data-framer-name=\"The All-in-One\"></p><h2 dir=\"auto\">认识一下 AI 项目经理 Alex</h2><p></p></div><div data-framer-name=\"Background\"><p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"397\" height=\"322\" src=\"https://framerusercontent.com/images/aYhFE5z0YrjieJ8h7I90mdZZ4.p