r-name=\"Background\"><p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"397\" height=\"322\" src=\"https://framerusercontent.com/images/aYhFE5z0YrjieJ8h7I90mdZZ4.png?width=397&height=322\" alt=\"\"></p><div data-framer-name=\"Gradient+Blur\"><p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1618\" height=\"970\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) max((100vw - 264px) / 2, 1px), (min-width: 810px) and (max-width: 1199.98px) calc(100vw - 96px), (max-width: 809.98px) calc(100vw - 32px)\" srcset=\"https://framerusercontent.com/images/hzzbCTKmJMAQFstLO5bKyXByFb4.png?scale-down-to=512&width=1618&height=970 512w,https://framerusercontent.com/images/hzzbCTKmJMAQFstLO5bKyXByFb4.png?scale-down-to=1024&width=1618&height=970 1024w,https://framerusercontent.com/images/hzzbCTKmJMAQFstLO5bKyXByFb4.png?width=1618&height=970 1618w\" src=\"https://framerusercontent.com/images/hzzbCTKmJMAQFstLO5bKyXByFb4.png?width=1618&height=970\" alt=\"\"></p></div></div><div data-framer-name=\"Bento Header\"><p data-framer-component-type=\"RichTextContainer\" data-framer-name=\"Designed to help you focus on what matters most—collaboration, clarity, and action.\"></p><h3 dir=\"auto\">阅读代理之间以及与您的团队之间任何任务的完整对话线索。 查看所采取的每个操作的带时间戳的日志。 没有什么在黑暗中运行。</h3><p></p></div></div></section></div></div>"}